# Simple Wait Test

Test that wait/evaluate commands work correctly.

## Test 1: Navigate to example.com
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_navigate",
  "params": {
    "url": "https://example.com"
  }
}
```

## Test 2: Wait 2 seconds
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_evaluate",
  "params": {
    "script": "() => new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 2000))"
  }
}
```

## Test 3: Get page title
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_evaluate",
  "params": {
    "script": "() => document.title"
  }
}
```

## Test 4: Get visible text
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_get_visible_text",
  "params": {}
}
```

## Test 5: Take screenshot
```mcp
{
  "tool": "playwright_screenshot",
  "params": {
    "name": "after-wait-test"
  }
}
```
